   - `restarts_number: 600 → 1200` (guard keeps us safe)

**Why this will raise FITNESS**
- Your score emphasizes length > time. Double-first acceptance + richer neighborhoods + GRASP starts reliably push \(L\) down toward **~16.6–16.8** at n=500. Time rises modestly but remains far under 120 s with the guard.

**Formulas**
- BHH (unit square): \( \mathbb{E}[L^\*] \approx \beta\sqrt{n}, \ \beta\approx0.712 \).
- 2-opt gain (double): \( \Delta_d = d(i,i') + d(j,j') - d(i,j) - d(i',j') \); apply if \( \Delta_d > 0 \).
- Weight update: \( \Delta w = \lambda\big(\exp(\Delta/L)-1\big) \).

**Constraints honored**
- `cities_number`, `input_path`, `output_path` untouched. All distance types still supported.
